      "span_text": "Although there are specific instances where an expert is likely to be more accurate (Dejaegar et al, 2012) there are situations where models can allow reduction in situational and human biases.  found unaided-estimates to be inaccurate, demonstrating a positive correlation between the use of intuition and the percentage of projects overrunning their estimates."
